data.description: Rarely available, spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom oasis nestled on an expansive corner lot of nearly half an acre. This remarkable property is a nature lover's paradise, boasting lush greenery and an abundance of trees and plants both in the front of the house and throughout the generous backyard. Mature trees and beautifully landscaped gardens create a picturesque setting, providing a sense of peace and tranquility. Well-maintained and thoughtfully designed interior. Creatively use additional rooms for a home office or gym. The backyard is a haven offering ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding amidst the natural beauty that surrounds you. The large lot size provides endless opportunities for expansion, a pool, or any other outdoor project you may have in mind.
